Qatar Masters (chess24.com) [7] 2023.10.18
C77 Ruy Lopez, four knights (Tarrasch) variation

00:00 Hello Everyone!

Magnus Carlsen and Hikaru Nakamura top the field for the Qatar Masters, a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 11–20 October 2023 in Lusail, Qatar. The prize fund is $110,000.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.qatarchess.qa
